orders

Class StoreOrder

  • java.lang.Object
    • orders.StoreOrder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Customizable

    public class StoreOrder
extends java.lang.Object
implements Customizable
    The StoreOrder class deals with storing orders made from coffee or donut orders. The class is capable of adding and removing orders and knows when its list is empty to prevent invalid commands with an empty list.
    Author:
    Jah C. Speed, Abe Vitangcol
